title: Ultimate Doctor Who eBook Collection 2013
description:
In this torrent, you will find the very best and most complete collection of Doctor Who related eBooks ever compiled into one torrent batch.

Utilizing resources from a half dozen other torrents I've found online, I've painstakingly worked through to find the best quality versions for any duplicates I found and even took the measure of putting them into chronological order according to the Doctor Who Reference Guide page!

Included in this torrent are eBooks for:

1) Doctor Who Handbooks Doctors 1-6
2) TARGET novelizations for the original series AND spin-offs!
3) BBC Books releases for the New Adventures
4) BBC Books releases for the "Missing" Adventures
5) BBC Books releases for the Eighth Doctor
6) Virgin Books
7) Telos Novellas
8) Other various publications

All of them have been put into their own respective folders by category.
